tips.game.1: Want infinte ammo in survival? give +1 ammo by commands. (Example: scoreboard players add @s ak47 1)
tips.game.2: This addon was made with love. And toxicity.
tips.game.4: Shooting your weapons whilst airborne is a bad idea.
tips.game.5: You are accurate whilst standing, but you are most accurate when crouching.
tips.game.6: Silencers make your shots quieter and will confuse enemies and wonder where the shot came from. However, silencers may boost or buff your gun stats depending on the gun.
tips.game.7: Your first shots are ALWAYS accurate. Thank you, Azoz!
tips.game.8: Actual Guns came out on July 29, 2019.
tips.game.10: Obtain skins by inserting the following command (!skin [gunname] [number]) / (!skin ak47 2)
tips.game.11: Enhancing your guns has no drawbacks at all.
